<div class="privacy-policy">
  <h1 class="policy-title">Privacy Policy for ANC App</h1>

  <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: January 05, 2025</p>

  <section class="policy-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Introduction</h2>
    <p class="section-content">This Privacy Policy describes how the ANC App ("we", "our", or "app") collects, uses, and handles your information. Our app provides both public content (newsletters, YouTube videos, church website access) and protected content (prayer requests) for our church community. We are committed to protecting your privacy while providing these spiritual and community services.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">App Structure and Access</h2>
    <p class="section-content">Our app consists of two types of content:</p>

    <div class="content-types">
      <div class="public-content">
        <h3 class="content-title">Public Content (No Authentication Required)</h3>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Church newsletters and images</li>
          <li>Public YouTube videos</li>
          <li>Church website access</li>
          <li>Other general church information</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="protected-content">
        <h3 class="content-title">Protected Content (Phone Authentication Required)</h3>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Prayer requests</li>
          <li>Prayer-related interactions</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Information We Collect</h2>
    <div class="info-block">
      <h3 class="subsection-title">1. Authentication Information (For Prayer Request Access Only)</h3>
      <ul class="info-list">
        <li>Phone number (only collected when accessing prayer requests)</li>
        <li>Authentication tokens for prayer request access</li>
        <li>Basic device information for authenticated sessions</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="info-block">
      <h3 class="subsection-title">2. Prayer Request Content (Authenticated Users Only)</h3>
      <ul class="info-list">
        <li>Prayer requests and related content</li>
        <li>User preferences related to prayer requests</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="info-block">
      <h3 class="subsection-title">3. Basic Usage Information</h3>
      <ul class="info-list">
        <li>App performance metrics</li>
        <li>Crash reports</li>
        <li>Basic analytics for app improvement</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <div class="info-block">
      <h3 class="subsection-title">Public Content Usage</h3>
      <ul class="info-list">
        <li>Displaying church newsletters</li>
        <li>Showing public YouTube videos</li>
        <li>Providing church website access</li>
        <li>These features do not require personal information</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="info-block">
      <h3 class="subsection-title">Protected Content Usage</h3>
      <ul class="info-list">
        <li>Authenticating users for prayer request access</li>
        <li>Managing and protecting prayer request content</li>
        <li>Ensuring secure access to private content</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Data Storage and Security</h2>
    <div class="info-block">
      <ul class="info-list">
        <li>Phone numbers and prayer requests are stored with encryption</li>
        <li>Public content is cached locally for performance</li>
        <li>Authentication data is handled using secure protocols</li>
        <li>Access to prayer request data is restricted to authorized users</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="section-content">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information. The only personal information we collect is:</p>
    <div class="info-block">
      <ul class="info-list">
        <li>Phone numbers for prayer request authentication</li>
        <li>The prayer requests themselves</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="section-content">All other app features access only public content that requires no personal information.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="section-content">Our app integrates with several third-party services:</p>
    <div class="info-block">
      <ul class="info-list">
        <li>YouTube (for public video content)</li>
        <li>Church website linking</li>
        <li>Authentication services (for prayer requests only)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="section-content">Each service has its own privacy policy. No personal information is shared with these services except as needed for authentication.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Your Rights</h2>
    <div class="info-block">
      <ul class="info-list">
        <li>Access your prayer request history</li>
        <li>Update or delete your prayer requests</li>
        <li>Remove your phone number from authentication</li>
        <li>Use public features without providing any personal information</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Security Measures</h2>
    <div class="info-block">
      <ul class="info-list">
        <li>Phone verification for prayer request access</li>
        <li>Encrypted storage of private content</li>
        <li>Public content is served securely but without personal data collection</li>
        <li>Regular security updates</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="section-content">Our app's public content is available to all users. The prayer request feature, which requires phone authentication, is not intended for users under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="section-content">We may update this Privacy Policy as needed. You will be notified of any material changes through the app.</p>
  </section>

